WEBVTT

00:00.178 --> 00:02.416
<i>Previously on "Better Call Saul..."</i>

00:02.828 --> 00:04.549
Why were you working against me?

00:04.653 --> 00:06.062
You're not a real lawyer!

00:06.521 --> 00:10.049
Now that I'm doing the job
alone, I get the full 1500.

00:10.111 --> 00:11.166
I can get more pills.

00:11.221 --> 00:13.045
If you're gonna be a
criminal, do your homework.

00:13.308 --> 00:15.925
Thanks for not heading
to the Bahamas with this.

00:16.011 --> 00:18.311
- What are you doing?
- "The right thing."

00:18.430 --> 00:20.647
Whatever it was, did you
get it out of your system?

00:20.765 --> 00:21.764
<i>Yep, all gone.</i>

00:21.900 --> 00:23.099
<i>(Kim) The Sandpiper case?</i>

00:23.185 --> 00:24.601
<i>It's getting too big for HHM.</i>

00:24.686 --> 00:25.652
What are you talking about?

00:25.770 --> 00:27.570
I'm talking about there's
an office in Santa Fe

00:27.656 --> 00:28.805
with your name on it.

00:32.910 --> 00:35.578
[ <i> "Funny How Time Slips Away"</i> plays]

00:43.088 --> 00:45.588
♪ Well, hello, there ♪

00:47.509 --> 00:52.595
♪ My, it's been a long, long time ♪

00:56.184 --> 00:59.152
♪ How am I doin'? ♪

00:59.187 --> 01:05.325
♪ Oh, I guess that I'm doin' fine ♪

01:05.360 --> 01:06.676
[Switch clicks]

01:07.712 --> 01:11.865
♪ It's been so long now ♪

01:11.917 --> 01:14.951
♪ And it seems that ♪

01:14.953 --> 01:20.623
♪ It was only yesterday ♪

01:20.675 --> 01:24.711
♪ Gee, ain't it funny ♪

01:24.763 --> 01:29.883
♪ How time slips away ♪

01:29.935 --> 01:33.219
♪ Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh ♪

01:33.271 --> 01:34.470
♪ Ooh ♪

01:34.472 --> 01:37.891
♪ Gotta go now ♪

01:37.943 --> 01:43.363
♪ Guess I'll see you around ♪

01:46.952 --> 01:49.986
♪ Don't know when, though ♪

01:49.988 --> 01:51.905
♪ Never know when I'll be back in town ♪

01:51.957 --> 01:53.489
Good night, ladies. Get home safe.

01:53.542 --> 01:55.909
See you later, Gene. Good night.

01:59.381 --> 02:02.382
♪ But remember ♪

02:02.417 --> 02:06.002
♪ What I tell you ♪

02:06.004 --> 02:11.558
♪ That, in time, you're gonna pay ♪

02:11.593 --> 02:15.845
♪ And it's surprising ♪

02:15.897 --> 02:21.017
♪ How time slips away ♪

02:21.052 --> 02:25.755
♪ Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh ♪

02:25.790 --> 02:28.391
