[Exhales sharply]

02:52.934 --> 02:55.051
No, no, no, no!

02:55.053 --> 02:56.886
[Grunts] God damn it!

02:56.938 --> 02:57.887
No!

02:57.889 --> 03:00.306
Oh, c-come on.

03:00.358 --> 03:02.725
[Grunting]

03:02.777 --> 03:05.278
Hey! Hey!

03:06.898 --> 03:08.948
Somebody!

03:15.073 --> 03:18.825
[Panting]

03:59.334 --> 04:00.283
[Banging on door]

04:00.335 --> 04:01.534
Hey!

04:01.586 --> 04:03.453
Hey!

04:05.790 --> 04:07.457
Hey!

04:07.459 --> 04:10.126
[Groans]

04:10.178 --> 04:11.711
[Sighs]

04:11.763 --> 04:15.515
[Panting]

04:37.455 --> 04:39.155
[Sighs]

04:56.841 --> 04:58.758
[Clock ticking]

04:58.810 --> 05:01.811
